{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"b19ef138-f368-455f-9181-5166e7d3bb4e","content":"No files found in the working directory — I'll walk you through the conversion directly.\n\n## Converting to Compiled Bindings\n\nAdd `x:DataType` to your `ContentPage` root element, pointing at your ViewModel:\n\n```xml\n<ContentPage xmlns=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/dotnet/2021/maui\"\n             xmlns:x=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2009/xaml\"\n             xmlns:vm=\"clr-namespace:YourApp.ViewModels\"\n             x:DataType=\"vm:SettingsViewModel\"\n             x:Class=\"YourApp.Views.SettingsPage\">\n\n    <VerticalStackLayout Padding=\"20\" Spacing=\"15\">\n\n        <Picker Title=\"Theme\"\n                SelectedItem=\"{Binding Theme}\" />\n\n        <Switch IsToggled=\"{Binding NotificationsEnabled}\" />\n\n        <Slider Minimum=\"8\" Maximum=\"32\"\n                Value=\"{Binding FontSize}\" />\n\n    </VerticalStackLayout>\n</ContentPage>\n```\n\n**Key change:** the single addition of `x:DataType=\"vm:SettingsViewModel\"` on the root element. This enables compiled bindings for every `{Binding}` on the page (and inherited by child elements).\n\n## Catching Binding Errors at Build Time\n\nCompiled bindings are validated by the XAML compiler. To ensure errors surface as **build failures**:\n\n1. **Keep `x:DataType` set** — misspelled or missing properties (e.g., `{Binding Themee}`) now produce **compiler error XC0045**.\n\n2. **Enable warnings-as-errors** *(recommended)* in your `.csproj`:\n   ```xml\n   <PropertyGroup>\n     <TreatWarningsAsErrors>true</TreatWarningsAsErrors>\n     <!-- or target only binding warnings: -->\n     <WarningsAsErrors>XC0045;XC0022</WarningsAsErrors>\n   </PropertyGroup>\n   ```\n\n3. **Opt out selectively** — if a binding must be resolved at runtime (e.g., dynamic context), use `x:DataType=\"\"` on that specific element to disable compiled bindings locally.\n\n**Result:** A typo like `{Binding Themee}` will now fail the build instead of silently failing at runtime.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"0a661e84-6e8f-4f49-a721-885dd4165243","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"No files found. The user is asking a general question about converting a MAUI page to use compiled bindings. Let me provide guidance based on their description.","outputTokens":601,"requestId":"110E:19B167:C06D4C:E08488:69FE8546"},"id":"811b787b-c795-422f-8b34-d76bfa21047f","timestamp":"2026-05-09T00:52:35.586Z","parentId":"3c084e03-cd01-4004-a03f-800be38a50de"}
